    <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> SimpleToolHub.site may use cookies to store information about visitors' preferences, record user-specific information on which pages the user accesses or visits, customize web page content based on visitors' browser type or other information that the visitor sends via their browser.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use the Information</h2>

<p>
    The information collected is used to enhance the visitor's experience when using our website, to display personalized content, and possibly to serve advertisements tailored to their interests.
</p>

